items.question: Is there an official Seedance 2.0 App?
items.answer: Currently, Seedance 2.0 does not have a standalone official app. It exists primarily as an API and web service. BabyBoogey is the most convenient web interface to use it on mobile, offering an app-like experience without taking up storage space.

items.question: What photo formats does Seedance 2.0 support?
items.answer: Supports mainstream formats like JPG, PNG, WEBP. We recommend uploading clear full-body or half-body photos without facial obstructions for the best skeletal recognition and generation results.
